Initial Setup:\
1. Create directory for app ("mkdir project_muselon") and navigate there ("cd project_muselon")\
2. Create virtual environment ("virtualenv venv")\
3. Activate virtual environment ("source venv/bin/activate")\
4. Install Flask ("pip install flask")\
5. Create directory for Python module ("mkdir muselon") and navigate there ("cd muselon")\
6. Create static and template directories ("mkdir static", "mkdir templates")\
